### ========== 先登录获取 Session ==========
# 把密码换成你控制台显示的随机密码
POST http://localhost:8081/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=user&password=9d7c6516-beca-4255-bca0-2a70a44f6038

> {%
    client.test("登录成功", function() {
        client.assert(response.status === 200 || response.status === 302, "登录失败");
    });
%}
### 1. 测试 hello 接口
GET http://localhost:8081/hello

### 2. 测试 about 接口
GET http://localhost:8081/about

